sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as Gateway
    participant F as File Metadata Service
    participant O as Object Storage
    participant M as Chat Service

    C->>G: Request upload intent
    G->>F: Create upload metadata
    F-->>C: Upload target and file id
    C->>O: Upload binary
    C->>G: Submit attachment metadata
    G->>M: Send message with attachment ref
    M-->>G: Stored message
    G-->>C: Message accepted
